This sample hook renders a list of pictures as a small gallery

Prerequisite
------------------------------------
- Suggested extension: perfectlightbox (or similar)


How to use
------------------------------------
- Copy content of setup.txt into your template TS.
- Add this to typo3conf/localconf.php:

$GLOBALS['TYPO3_CONF_VARS']['EXTCONF']['file_list']['extraItemMarkerHook'][] = 'EXT:file_list/Samples/gallery/tx_filelist_gallery.php:tx_filelist_gallery';

- Add a plugin to your page and choose a directory containing pictures
